promo_txt: This is an accurate depiction of a bike, which should be instantly recognizable when compared with other illustrations. It has used a variety of different colours to make it visually appealing and demonstrates uniqueness, too. A lot of effort has gone into making the illustration appear instantly recognizable and to make it stand out when next to other illustrations.
I tried to pick a less obvious picture that used a variety of the lines, shapes and colours. The tools were fairly difficult to work with and I am not very artistic but I tried my best.
